*.keystore
# debug keystore is intentionally committed so every CI build signs with
# the same key — otherwise installing a new APK on top of the previous
# one fails with INSTALL_FAILED_UPDATE_INCOMPATIBLE (signature mismatch).
!app/debug.keystore

# Claude Code: personal/uncommitted variants are excluded; the shared
# CLAUDE.md and .claude/ folder are committed for everyone.
CLAUDE.local.md
.claude/settings.local.json
